Inspired by Technous Japan's game "Nekketsu Koukou Dodgeball Bu: Soccer Hen".

Based on retrogamelib (http://code.google.com/p/retrogamelib/) for screen and dialogs. 


How to play:
  P1: arrows (to move) + K (to kick), L (to attack), P (for pause)
  P2: F, G, H (to move) +  A (to kick), Z (to attack), R (for pause)



